TransactionsGrinder moduleÔÉÅ

class TransactionsGrinder.TransactionsGrinder(file_name, z3model_path='./Z3_models/', txt_path='./Examples/dafsm_txt/', json_path='./Examples/jsons/', log=True, logTime=False, non_stop=True, time_out=0)[source]ÔÉÅ

Bases: Logger

Processes transactions from a JSON file to generate Z3 models, handling pre-processing, grouping transactions, and executing Z3 models for verification.

Inherits from Logger for logging capabilities.

check_independant_sat()[source]ÔÉÅ

Checks the independent satisfiability of the model by verifying each transaction separately.

check_path_sat()[source]ÔÉÅ

Checks path satisfiability of the model by verifying the satisfiability of different paths through the FSM.
